 the operation (that is, produces the same output value\n    given the same input values). The last argument specifies the controller\n    as a list of labels and machine instructions, as in\n    section ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"5.1","href":"/sicp/5.1"},{"body":".\n  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p3","child":[{"body":"\n    To compute GCDs with this machine, we set the input registers, start the\n    machine, and examine the result when the simulation terminates:\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":2,"eval":true,"prependLength":266,"program":"chap=4&-MElihs4rjuGQAHvr2L78uakyFLMJQdmkrhZNGLqMvy6ajpm0hDlaT4slB7KctyfICt+baRsuJydrEsGzPBAE4q8KaMcOGYOvmGGOBYXiTGQPB4TaBFkJ6UmlCA3CYbwUInPe9KAoe5Afvo4iSHJ6kfjmdD2Lw77is0HBAgQGk0AZRkmbSuKPhZVkmlR-JOfpsqGcZszilgyLudZnm2T59kPgyPDPu5IA5rRyiQshb6oSAjhOnUPryHKdDqEOdYaI2xYcMKFwBVphjRbKC4dP8KSmp+aR6caNWueVrCVelfwuayWTETCMFTIBH7up1FZMbEEUsixkS9j1HTDdRRW-lGCUDdEM3euNrLuByBBctNo2xE0rRNb2ugLRCf6DouEljlmHSgLyOC8PY77Jd0vA4Fg9gMCAeCYu56ErrQ044LOACEx7cFlvydQp3GLs0yREO9LjZClNKhapaRYIjyMpclqWxIDU6RDOubg3jjTIrlxMKiDub44OKkXBtbCsC1WpnfRLzLe+rx4Lc5AM2lIG6ji22RGQrNA5K4sTDmbWVH1KFTe6MpYLLXqWL8ovq3BClrWNTITf1cGCgbchq7LsWLcuPOoZVV0jjdmsNETwNgz9AuIjLetvXDa4I-KuOo06-vohumK9JszQgAAKqsYCx+zXkvfMF5kte+zy3edIXFLNO60e+c2d5kS+RwxdBaXRDKbnj4bb40xI-w7PW+dS389wgto8L2u4GzGCN0H-A0P3WrZ9CGCK-Gzy9iqY+a+1U+ythTGXHYYYRvFM8fEmCYgAvDtVddmYu960+Tu79Od+QZ+Lm7JN08w5PZDmq37YC2NB2RIeXSRGJ9GjviTYAAlRYAA5KAAAJZOwUJZpxAKSK8FJ2aMzrgyIezdR44DZpggQgVWApx8mlJoyI8EjxLnZU4DkGRynIJQLA4YtDlmonQ7409HDcAIHQFhnp+I4AAI4qkaJDAcENb75jwCkFctcaFdnyj2d0SEMB0IYUw1gvDVAiFkWFeRTACrwX7Mo0hHAUzUN0aLVg8pFRljESoruaiLDMK-CoGUrUMYXDcfqGxzgXJ2JMbecxmM3S2OUaoj66iqCaJUKCHRwSEzwWTGqREZlAlM3rkbGg5ArBUCsK3Tm8Ue7Wj7jg302TcnYLZhPS0OtXQJPdAvHqS837myrBBcM+9IStI-jvRMfIOnPAPqUv+cYT7jgwA-WmHs8ZvxGSRQsCiSwNOGU0kWIhukTnrN2ZsZ0NmjQWfoxR-T+yHzDjhMZWZzYTPrFfZ++NNnSymfTbRczFzLgZAArEQCQAAHEADysc-mwOrueRBl5yR7BmhPOJFxylWEqVqOFBCqBELLiQ1JSLKEhSCRcRwYErG8FsN8AlthVB4s9B4x8jh7DMBbiSl